User Help Guide
1. Data Cleaning
File Structure: Place data files in DB (contains ADHD_DB and Control_DB).
Run Clean_EEG.py: Cleans data and saves it in Clean_DB.
2. EEG Analysis
Option A: BLAST

Run BLAST.py: Processes cleaned data, saves results in BLAST_DB. You can adjust time segments, overlap, and file name.
Option B: Order-Preserving Matching

Run Order_Preserving_Matching.py: Processes data, saves results in Order_Preserving_Matching. You can adjust downsampling rate and file name.
3. Classification
Run Classification.py: Specify result file name for classification and run the script.
